snippet.title: Amber Enterprises Ltd - Short Analysis
snippet.description:
Amber Enterprises is India’s largest contract manufacturer of fully built Room Air-Conditioner units with 23-24% market share in the Room Air Conditioner Market. The Top Management of Company is optimistic about the robust and positive demand outlook for Air Conditioners after the IMD forecasted scorching summer for India this year. Here is a short qualitative analysis of Amber Enterprises.

Key Points Covered :

0.00    Introduction

0:59    Robust Demand Outlook in scorching summer

02:10    Supply-side Challenges

03:17    Capacity & Capex Plans

04:04    Capital Raise to Fund Capex Plans

04:35    Big Boost by PLI Scheme

05:08    Conclusion
